Transforming Speech Into Action – Join Us

We’re building real-time speech technology that empowers accessibility, productivity, and live communication. We're looking for partners and investors to join us on this journey.

Request Investor Deck

The Problem & Opportunity

Every day, billions of words are spoken and lost. Our mission is to make them accessible, searchable, and useful—instantly. With live transcription powered by WebRTC and AI, we enable real-time speech-to-text for meetings, interviews, education, and beyond.

Why Now?

  • ✅ Working MVP with live transcription under 300ms latency
  • ✅ Built on cutting-edge tools (Groq, Whisper, WebRTC)
  • ✅ Early testers in education and content creation

What We’re Looking For

We’re seeking early investors, thought partners, and technical collaborators who believe in the power of voice-driven tools.

About Us

Alex Founder – Speech AI engineer, former product lead at StartupX
